{"tid":1190644,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"香港現場爵士樂推介","createTime":"2019-06-07T12:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:53.000Z","uid":201746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78402624eb37e677b44a411dc940d3291c02ed25","tid":1190644,"uid":201746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:20:23.000Z","msg":"以前我認為爵士樂呢樣嘢通常都係一樣深藏不露、閉門造車嘅興趣。大學時期嘅時候我開始接觸唔同嘅爵士樂手，然後去日本同外國二手市場瘋狂搜刮二手碟。直到宜家出黎做嘢開始對本土Live Jazz有興趣，有時都會去下例如Grappa's Cellar類型嘅Lounge，最正係不單只有Live band，嗰度請嘅vocal都好有質素。請問有冇爵士樂撚可以介紹下香港仲有邊度有現在爵士樂聽？"},{"pid":"83ce4f60e2df02a4566330c30d01aa6112bd58e4","tid":1190644,"uid":189092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"Peel Fresco, Sense 99, Wontonmeen, Visage One, Brew Note, Foxglove, Fringe Club"},{"pid":"b1fa187fcab323845cc80728500d9ab8d1482f97","tid":1190644,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"Ned Kelly ?"},{"pid":"00f3e3b05e219d15b1a91fa940d408de66712f13","tid":1190644,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"之前Ron Carter嚟香港，正到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9503b1bdb27dab2cbf72d93f833f0f3d0a7efaa","tid":1190644,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"Salon 10"}]}